Zhou Han a facut
in sfarsit o treaba buna.

638
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:58,580
Nu ar trebui sa ma bucur?

639
00:36:01,750 --> 00:36:04,679
Ai ceva vesti
de la Zhou Han?

640
